content: The actual answer is "not enough information". You should reason more rigorously. Now another claim is "There were less than 2,000 COVID-19 deaths in Iran with less than 25,000 confirmed infections during the pandemic , according to Iranian health authorities ." Evidences are ["according to Iranian health authorities , there had been 1,812 COVID-19 deaths in Iran with more than 23,049 confirmed infections ."]
